'''''High Winds''''' was an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Propaganda/Legends|propaganda]] [[Holodrama/Legends|holodrama]] staring [[Tetran Cowall]], a long-time rival of [[Garik Loran]]. The drama was about [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] tightrope walkers. It often featured the tightrope walkers plummeting to their [[Death/Legends|deaths]]. It was designed to show people that such uncommon behavior only ever caused trouble.

